title: Iraqis to vote in first election since I.S.
text:
Iraqis to vote in first election since I.S. 7:32am EDT - 02:01
For the first time since driving out Islamic State, Iraqis go to the polls on Saturday in an election that will shape attempts to heal the country's deep divisions and could shift the regional balance of power. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
